library(dplyr)
library(stringr)
ig_data=read.csv("C:/Users/sadsi/Documents/ig1.csv")

tags=ig_data$Hashtags

tags=as.data.frame(tags)

for(i in 1:nrow(tags)){tags[i,]=as.character(tags[i,])}

tags=cbind(matrix(c(1:100),nrow=100,ncol=1),tags)

colnames(tags)=c("No","word")
  
tags=tags%>%unnest_tokens(words,word)

count=c()
for(j in 1:100){count=rbind(count,nrow(tags[which(tags$No==j),]))}
ig=c()
ig=cbind(ig,ig_data$Followers)
ig=cbind(ig,gsub("hours","",ig_data$Time.since.posted))
count=as.data.frame(count)
ig=cbind(ig,count$V1)
ig=cbind(ig,ig_data$Likes)
colnames(ig)=c("Followers","Time","Hashtags","Likes")

ig=as.data.frame(ig)
ig$Followers=as.numeric(ig$Followers)
ig$Time=as.numeric(ig$Time)
ig$Hashtags=as.numeric(ig$Hashtags)
ig$Likes=as.numeric(ig$Likes)
x1 <- ig$Followers;
x2 <- ig$Time;
x3 <- ig$Hashtags;
y <- ig$Likes;

dum <- data.frame("ig$Likes"=y,"ig$Followers"=x1,"ig$Time"=x2,"ig$Hashtags"=x3)

attach(dum)

rm(x1,x2,x3,y)

pairs(dum) #分散圖矩陣

cor(dum) #各項相關系數

fm <- lm(ig$Likes~ig$Followers+ig$Time+ig$Hashtags, dum)

fmbd<-data.frame("x1"=ig$Followers,"x2"=ig$Time,"x3"=ig$Hashtags,"y"=ig$Likes,"y_hat"=fitted(fm),"residual"=resid(fm)) #線性迴歸的基本資料(Basic Data)
